      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 75,
      "y": 834,
      "width": 740,
      "height": 78,
      "text": "every runAgent/runOneShot spawn that does NOT pin cwd/homeDir (chat, brand-research,\nclassifier one-shots) gets an EMPTY per-run sandbox dir; cwd=sandbox, HOME=sandbox,\nremoved at run end. build/verify keep their explicit project dir (never overridden).\nbuildSubprocessEnv scrubs the inherited server path from PWD/OLDPWD/INIT_CWD, npm_*,\nand PATH segments under the CHECKOUT root only (never HOME - node lives under HOME on nvm/user hosts; its bin dir is preserved so the bare-node spawn resolves). settingSources:[] + the\nper-agent tool allow-list remain the primary gates; this removes the inherited-path vector.",
      "rawText": "every runAgent/runOneShot spawn that does NOT pin cwd/homeDir (chat, brand-research,\nclassifier one-shots) gets an EMPTY per-run sandbox dir; cwd=sandbox, HOME=sandbox,\nremoved at run end. build/verify keep their explicit project dir (never overridden).\nbuildSubprocessEnv scrubs the inherited server path from PWD/OLDPWD/INIT_CWD, npm_*,\nand PATH segments under the CHECKOUT root only (never HOME - node lives under HOME on nvm/user hosts; its bin dir is preserved so the bare-node spawn resolves). settingSources:[] + the\nper-agent tool allow-list remain the primary gates; this removes the inherited-path vector.",
